name: Benor Organics Private Limited
overview:
Desh’Se is a high quality brand of Organic food and non-food products from Benor Organics Pvt Ltd, based in India. It sells certified organic products online. Customers can place orders for organic food products such as cereals, lentils, spices and edible oils. The company is planning to expand its portfolio to offer organic preserves and spreads, tea and coffee, snacks, textiles and cosmetics.

Desh’Se sources fresh and natural products from dependable sources. These products are produced through traditional methods without the use of harmful chemicals and pesticides. Hence, they are 100% organic and healthy. Customers can order these products from the convenience of their home, and collect the order delivered direct to home.
